Selenium Class 5

Handling checkboxes and radiotbuttons:
--if you have only 1 checkbox or radiobutton-you can just click on it
-- if you have multiple choices- store them in List and loop through

DropDowns:
-- Dropdowns is a menu which gives us an opportunity to select one or more options

Types of DropDowns:
1) Single select
2) Multiple select

Handling dropdowns:
1)click on dropdown and click on the option
2)using Select class
    --in order to use the Select class we need to make sure our dropdown has a select tag

Selecting an option from a dropwdown can be done in 3 ways:
1) By index
2) By visible text
3) By value

Whenever you interact with multiple elements, you store them inside the container such as
    -List
    -Set

